---------------------------------------------------------------------
eBrainPool Plugin for OLSRD
by eBrain <ebrain@ebrain.in>
---------------------------------------------------------------------

This library needs olsrd v0.5.6-r7. It hasn't been tested on later versions. Download the source code for v0.5.6-r7 of olsrd and copy the root directory for this plugin under the lib directory of the olsrd source.

Installing

cd [olsrd-src]/lib/ebp-olsrd-plugin
make
make install

Configuration

Make changes to the /etc/olsrd.conf to enable this plugin and provide a username. A sample config is shown below.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
SAMPLE CONFIG
---------------------------------------------------------------------

adPlugin "olsrd_ebp.so.0.1"
{
                PlParam "Username" "Duffer@Desktop"
}

--------------------------------------------------------------------
